    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'd like to move V2 to root and keep the current under /v1/\r\nit needs to handle clean redirections. Github doesn't allow .htaccess and I would avoid any JavaScript redirection.\r\n\r\nPossibilities to explore:\r\n- ~html files with HTTP-REFRESH meta tag~\r\n- cloudflare\r\n\r\nWe need clean 301.",
